import { fade, makeStyles } from '@material-ui/core/styles'

export default makeStyles((theme) => ({
    root: {
        margin: theme.spacing(1),
        justify: 'space-between',
        alignItems: 'center',
        alignContent: 'center',
    },

    paper: {
        padding: theme.spacing(1),
        color: theme.palette.text.secondary,
    },
    item_first: {
        fontFamily: 'Inter',
        fontStyle: 'normal',
        fontWeight: 500,
        fontSize: '16px',
        lineHeight: '19px',

        width: '38px',
        height: '19px',
        left: '0px',
    },
    main: {
        fontWeight: 600,
        fontStyle: 'normal',
        fontFamily: 'Inter',
        fontSize: '30px',
        lineHeight: '36px',
        textAlign: 'center',
    },
    search: {

        justify:'center',
        height: '40px',
        width: '100%',
        border: '1px solid #E8E8E8',
        position: 'relative',
        background: '#F6F6F6',
        boxSizing: 'border-box',
        borderRadius: '100px',
    },

}))
